Summary: Properties and member variables of the FoldableGroup class, including allow_folding_all and resource_local_to_scene.

Property: allow_folding_all (bool): Controls whether all items in the group can be folded. Default: false.
Property: resource_local_to_scene (bool): Determines if the resource is local to the scene. Default: true (overrides Resource.resource_local_to_scene).
