Document: FoldableGroup
Path: godot/classes/class_foldablegroup.rst
Summary: Methods for accessing containers and expanded state in FoldableGroup.

Method: get_containers() → Array[FoldableContainer]
Returns an Array of FoldableContainer instances that have this FoldableGroup as their foldable_group property. This functions similarly to ButtonGroup but for FoldableContainers.

Method: get_expanded_container() → FoldableContainer
Returns the currently expanded FoldableContainer in the group.